{{News|September 21, 2016|HTTPS for links|As part of our effort to continually improve the wiki, we'd like to encourage the use of HTTPS for external links wherever possible. This is ''especially'' important for an article's [[Template:InfoBox homepage|homepage InfoBox]] link since it is prominently placed at the top of articles (and more likely to be clicked). Please verify the link supports HTTPS before substituting. Happy improvements!}}

{{News|February 27, 2016|Embedded Handbook|As of today, all parts of the Gentoo [[Embedded Handbook]] have been migrated to the wiki. Feel free to add new embedded boards (such as Pine64 and the Raspberry Pi Zero) using the [[Gentoo_Wiki:Article_Blueprints/Hardware/Embedded|Embedded article blueprint]].}}

{{News|January 31, 2016|USEflag template update|The {{Tl|USEflag}} template has been updated from using static tables to use the newly implemented [https://packages.gentoo.org packages.g.o] API. This enables the USE flag sections of articles to dynamically load updates as the Portage tree evolves. Contributors can learn more of the details by reading [[Gentoo Wiki:Template Migrations/USEflag|the latest template migration article]].}}

