<h2 id="Getting_started"><i class="fa fa-road fa-fw"></i>&nbsp;Getting started</h2>
Anyone is welcome to edit or create pages on this wiki.

Before making your first edit or creating your first new page, please consult the [[Help:Contents|Help page]]. It also links to the [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Contents MediaWiki User's Guide] which contains information about how the wiki software works.

If you think there is something we can improve, please let us know on the [[Gentoo_Wiki:Feedback|Feedback page]].

Should you have any questions ''related to using or editing the wiki'', you can always join our {{IRC|gentoo-wiki|mode=webchat}} IRC channel on Freenode or email us at [mailto:wiki@gentoo.org wiki@gentoo.org].

'''Please note''': If you need general Gentoo support, please get in touch with our [https://www.gentoo.org/support/ support community] instead.

